Image.png" alt=3D"QuantityVariable[&quot;SLG&quot;, &quot;Unitless&quot;] =
=3D=3D (QuantityVariable[&quot;1B&quot;, &quot;Unitless&quot;] + 2*Quantity=
Variable[&quot;2B&quot;, &quot;Unitless&quot;] + 3*QuantityVariable[&quot;3=
B&quot;, &quot;Unitless&quot;] + 4*QuantityVariable[&quot;HR&quot;, &quot;U=
nitless&quot;])/QuantityVariable[&quot;AB&quot;, &quot;Unitless&quot;]" tit=
